<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('layouts/header') -%>
<body>

<!--Navbar-->
<%- include('layouts/nav') -%>
<!-- Navbar -->


<div class="container p-5" style="margin-top:90px; margin-bottom: 60px;">
    <h1 class="display-6">Reviews Help</h1>
    <p class="lead">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Accusamus debitis inventore non quisquam repellendus sunt unde vero voluptatum. Assumenda exercitationem, iure molestias officiis porro quae rem similique suscipit vero vitae.
